# Changelog

## 0.8.0
- Fix memory leaks
- Valgrind make target
- Parse and load schedule files

## 0.7.1
- Implement cross-axis and main-axis alignment
- Implement flex-grow and weight based stretching

## 0.7.0
- Cleaner scrollable content abstraction
- Robust scaling and resizing support
- Remove time of day horizontal indicator
- Remove custom font
- Dead code

## 0.6.3
- Rewrite flexbox layout
- Time of day horizontal indicator opacity improvements

## 0.6.2
- Fix window size now growing automatically using tiling managers

## 0.6.1
- Custom font scaling tweaks

## 0.6.0
- Custom font
- Time of day horizontal indicator

## 0.5.0
- Support space between items
- Scaling and resizing support

## 0.4.0
- Initial flexbox layout implementation
- Support align items center, justify content center, align items end and start

## 0.3.1
- Fix scrolling beyond limits
- Fix time not being displayed correctly
- Windows support (untested)

## 0.3.0
- Scrollable list using mouse wheel
- Natural scrolling

## 0.2.0
- Scrollable list of events

## 0.1.0
- Open window
- List all events
